  "text": "## OpenTelemetry Span Creation Patterns Across Prometheus and Grafana\n\n### Prometheus Patterns\n\n**Tracer Initialization and Provider Setup:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:tracing/tracing.go` - Central tracing management through `Manager` type and `buildTracerProvider()` function\n- Initializes TracerProvider with SDK: `tracesdk.NewTracerProvider()` with batcher, sampler, and resource configuration\n- Sets global tracer provider via `otel.SetTracerProvider()` and error handler via `otel.SetErrorHandler()`\n- Uses both gRPC (`otlptracegrpc.NewClient`) and HTTP (`otlptracehttp.NewClient`) OTLP exporters based on configuration\n\n**Span Creation:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:1919` - `ctx, span := otel.Tracer(\"\").Start(ctx, stats.InnerEvalTime.SpanOperation()\" eval \"+reflect.TypeOf(expr).String())`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:scrape/scrape.go:748` - `ctx, span := otel.Tracer(\"\").Start(ctx, \"Scrape\", trace.WithSpanKind(trace.SpanKindClient))`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:rules/group.go:515` - `ctx, sp := otel.Tracer(\"\").Start(ctx, \"rule\")`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:storage/remote/client.go:290` and `402` - Remote storage operations with span kind configuration\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:storage/remote/queue_manager.go:600` - `ctx, span := otel.Tracer(\"\").Start(ctx, \"Remote Metadata Send Batch\")`\n\n**Span Attributes:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:250,1922` - `span.SetAttributes(attribute.String(queryTag, q.stmt.String()))` and operation names\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:rules/group.go:516` - `sp.SetAttributes(attribute.String(\"name\", rule.Name()))`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:storage/remote/queue_manager.go:603-608` - Multiple attributes including metadata count, try count, remote name/URL\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:2328,2334` - Float64 and String attributes for values\n\n**Span Events and Context:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:1100-1109` - `span.AddEvent(\"expand start\", trace.WithAttributes(...))` and `span.AddEvent(\"expand end\", ...)`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:1100` - `span := trace.SpanFromContext(ctx)` for retrieving existing span from context\n\n**Span Error Handling:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:rules/group.go:537,567,587` - `sp.SetStatus(codes.Error, err.Error())`\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:storage/remote/queue_manager.go:621` - `span.RecordError(err)`\n\n**Span Lifecycle:**\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:promql/engine.go:1920` - `defer span.End()` for proper cleanup\n- File: `prometheus/prometheus:scrape/scrape.go:749` - Defer span.End() immediately after span creation\n\n### Grafana Patterns\n\n**Tracer Initialization:**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/api/api.go:59` - Global tracer: `var tracer = otel.Tracer(\"github.com/grafana/grafana/pkg/api\")`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/infra/tracing/tracing.go` - Complete `TracingService` implementation managing tracer provider lifecycle\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/metrics.go:233` - `tracer := otel.GetTracerProvider().Tracer(\"dashboard-converter\")`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/iam/pkg/reconcilers/folder_reconciler.go:78` - `tracer := otel.GetTracerProvider().Tracer(\"iam-folder-reconciler\")`\n\n**Span Creation with Attributes:**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/api/dashboard.go:50` - `ctx, span := tracer.Start(c.Req.Context(), \"api.isDashboardStarredByUser\")`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/metrics.go:234-238` - Span creation with inline attributes: `tracer.Start(ctx, \"dashboard.conversion\", trace.WithAttributes(...))`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/iam/pkg/reconcilers/folder_reconciler.go:79-85` - `tracer.Start(ctx, \"folder.reconcile\", trace.WithAttributes(attribute.String(\"action\", ...), attribute.String(\"folder.uid\", ...), ...))`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/infra/httpclient/httpclientprovider/tracing_middleware.go:28` - `tracer.Start(req.Context(), \"HTTP Outgoing Request\", trace.WithSpanKind(trace.SpanKindClient))`\n\n**Span Attributes (Post-Creation):**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/metrics.go:244,246` - `span.SetAttributes(attribute.String(\"dashboard.uid\", info.uid))` and `span.SetAttributes(attribute.Int(\"source.schema_version\", int(schemaVer)))`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/v1beta1_to_v2alpha1.go:32,38,46,58,63,72,80` - Extensive use of SetAttributes with various attribute types\n\n**Error Recording and Status Setting:**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/metrics.go:264-267` - `span.SetStatus(codes.Error, err.Error())` on error, `span.SetStatus(codes.Ok, \"conversion successful\")` on success\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/iam/pkg/reconcilers/folder_reconciler.go:96-97` - `span.RecordError(err)` followed by `span.SetStatus(codes.Error, \"validation failed\")`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/iam/pkg/reconcilers/zanzana_service.go:53,73,91,97,129,150` - Consistent error status setting patterns\n\n**Context and Span Management Utilities:**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/conversion/tracing_helper.go:16` - Helper function `TracingStart()` that retrieves tracer from context and creates spans with attributes\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/infra/tracing/tracing.go:309` - Tracer provider management: `ots.Tracer = otel.GetTracerProvider().Tracer(\"component-main\")`\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/infra/tracing/tracing.go:437` - Similar helper pattern: `trace.SpanFromContext(ctx).TracerProvider().Tracer(instrumentationScope).Start(ctx, name, trace.WithAttributes(attributes...))`\n\n**Span Kind Configuration:**\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/middleware/request_tracing.go:111` - `trace.WithSpanKind(trace.SpanKindServer)` for HTTP server spans\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/infra/httpclient/httpclientprovider/tracing_middleware.go:28` - `trace.WithSpanKind(trace.SpanKindClient)` for HTTP client spans\n- File: `grafana/grafana:pkg/storage/unified/sql/db/otel/otel.go:48` - `spanOptKindClient = trace.WithSpanKind(trace.SpanKindClient)`\n\n### Common OpenTelemetry Imports Across Both Projects\n\nBoth repositories consistently use:\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel` - Main OTEL package for tracer provider and global setup\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace` - Span and tracer interfaces, span kind constants\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/attribute` - Attribute key-value construction\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/codes` - Status codes (Error, Ok)\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/trace` - TracerProvider SDK implementation\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/otlp/*` - OTLP exporters (gRPC and HTTP variants)\n\n### Key Differences\n\n**Prometheus:** Uses empty string tracer `otel.Tracer(\"\")` consistently across codebase, centralizes tracer provider management in dedicated `tracing` package, uses SDK-level TracerProvider configuration.\n\n**Grafana:** Uses instrumentation scope-specific tracers (e.g., `\"github.com/grafana/grafana/pkg/api\"`), retrieves TracerProvider from global state via `otel.GetTracerProvider()`, provides helper utilities for conditional span creation, more extensive use of span attributes set at creation time via `trace.WithAttributes()`."
